		<bioghist encodinganalog="545">
			<head>Biographical History</head>
			
		<p>Michael Lewis, son of journalist Dorothy Thompson and writer Sinclair Lewis.  Stage and screen actor.</p></bioghist>
		
		<scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
			<head>Scope and Contents of the Collection</head>
			<p>The Michael Lewis Collection consists mainly of photographs -- head shots and photos of Lewis in various roles ranging from Don John the Bastard ("Much Ado About Nothing" to a role in "The Virginian."  There is a single clipping, a photograph of his parents.</p>
		</scopecontent>
		
